Package: SpoTubeR
Type: Package
Title: Match Spotify Songs with YouTube Music Videos
Authors@R: c(
    person("Úna", "Gogstetter", email = "ugogstetter@smith.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Samantha", "Kotkin", email = "skotkin@smith.edu", role = ("aut")))
Maintainer: <ugogstetter@smith.edu>
Description: Match Spotify songs with their existing YouTube music videos and compare their characteristics. Get information about their genres, popularity, record labels, release years, and more. To learn more about the Spotify API, see <https://developer.spotify.com/documentation/web-api/>. To learn more about the YouTube API, see <https://developers.google.com/youtube/v3/>.
